data.description: Absolutely Beautiful!! Located near Coral Gables and Coconut Grove.... Corner lot with new concrete driveway. Per Seller: New roof (2016), new impact resistant windows (2016), new kitchen with wood cabinets & granite counter tops (2016), new bathroom (2021), Stainless Steel appliances (2016), central A/C (2016). Exterior lighting, cozy patio, 1 covered car port with resealed stamped concrete driveway. Fence all around property. Must See!!!
